{"tid":1416542,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大家檢討可唔可以唔好打緊個時檢討","createTime":"2019-08-05T15:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T15:19:09.000Z","uid":103960,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"09078e4ea7004c60e7ac7c27d2768930ea009710","tid":1416542,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:12:53.000Z","msg":"好多晚都係咁<br />\n發夢嘅人同連登冷氣軍師好似係平行時空一樣<br />\n你地今晚睇完新聞 可能有好撚多意見急住想講<br />\n你有無諗過 前線同現場人士根本唔會得閒睇你講咩<br />\n攰到狗一樣 翻到屋企仲要比你地質問<br />\n「改口號啦」「唔好玩火」「仲睇唔睇民意」<br />\n<br />\n第二日你地咩都討論完<br />\n結果係咩？<br />\n前線嘅人會唔會參與到討論？<br />\n<br />\n另一樣野係<br />\n翻到屋企命要俾你地班冷氣軍師檢討<br />\n左一句係唔係無腦 <br />\n右一句係唔係唔撚識<br />\n切身處地會係咩感受？<br />\n尊重係唔係唔識？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0160a83f0cf7f490741a9ac21f1134fbe2bdc0cf","tid":1416542,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:13:08.000Z","msg":"搵人幫手推"},{"pid":"47ec45a663d5c599a62c0fa0c6087a9be287ca9b","tid":1416542,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:13:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9a45f437aa8b2efc26feb9d5eee0a0f9024cd5d","tid":1416542,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:14:52.000Z","msg":"其實第二日再一齊檢討<br />\n大家禮貌少少就得<br />\n<br />\n起碼唔會有你地講無前線講<br />\n大家無咁攰 會比較理性討論"},{"pid":"1092508e83a4c9d48aba43c12588fa3ad4b954e2","tid":1416542,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:15:37.000Z","msg":"唔好只係俾負皮 <br />\n留言啦"},{"pid":"f29764bfc14eff53f8b0d2a9065c797a09ff7261","tid":1416542,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:16:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1610669d39223a49ce6ba76ee2fcff6ff7644485","tid":1416542,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:16:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20fefbc60a1e26dad7788234e7a80b8a0aac2a41","tid":1416542,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply